import React from 'react'; import { Bell, MessageSquare, User, ChevronRight, Calendar, FileCheck, AlertCircle, Clock, BookOpen, Plane } from 'lucide-react'; const StudentDashboard = () => { const user = 'Richard Pokhrel'; // Dynamically fetched or passed as a prop const notifications = [ { id: 1, type: 'deadline', message: 'University of Toronto application deadline in 5 days', time: '2 hours ago' }, { id: 2, type: 'document', message: 'Your IELTS score report has been verified', time: '1 day ago' }, { id: 3, type: 'update', message: 'Visa application status updated', time: '2 days ago' } ]; const priorityTasks = [ { id: 1, title: 'Complete University Application', description: 'Submit pending documents for University of Toronto', status: 'urgent', deadline: '5 days remaining' }, { id: 2, title: 'Book IELTS Test', description: 'Required for final application submission', status: 'pending', deadline: '2 weeks remaining' }, { id: 3, title: 'Submit Passport Copy', description: 'Required for visa processing', status: 'pending', deadline: '1 week remaining' } ]; const applicationStages = [ { label: 'Applications submitted', count: 2, icon: }, { label: 'Offers received', count: 1, icon: }, { label: 'Pending documents', count: 3, icon: }, { label: 'Visa applications', count: 0, icon: } ]; return (
{/* Header Section */}

Hi, {user}!

Welcome back, we're happy to have you here!

{/* Application Progress */}

Application Progress

{applicationStages.map((stage, index) => (
{stage.icon} {stage.count}

{stage.label}

))}
{/* Quick Actions */}

Quick Actions

{/* Priority Tasks */}

Priority Tasks

{priorityTasks.map(task => (

{task.title}

{task.deadline}

{task.description}

))}
{/* Notifications */}

Recent Updates

{notifications.map(notification => (

{notification.message}

{notification.time}
))}
); }; export default StudentDashboard;
